Program: Great Lives
Title: Martha Gellhorn
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00772zs
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 10 Jun 2016
A typical story in Popbitch is usually about 90 words. This probably explains why its editor Camilla Wright has chosen Martha Gellhorn as her Great Life. Gellhorn wrote at length about the Spanish Civil War, the Second World War and Vietnam. Biographer Caroline Moorhead joins presenter Matthew Parris to dissect and debate a brilliant and complicated life. Show less